%2C+165&amp;rft.pub=A.K.+Peters&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F814380325&amp;rft.isbn=1439875383&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldcat.org%2Foclc%2F814380325&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AVideo+game+writing\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.stormthecastle.com/video-game-design/writing-a-video-game-script.htm\">\"Flowchart a video game script\"</a>. <i>Storm The Castle</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20170922213346/http://www.stormthecastle.com/video-game-design/writing-a-video-game-script.htm\">Archived</a> from the original on 2017-09-22<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-09-25</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Storm+The+Castle&amp;rft.atitle=Flowchart+a+video+game+script&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stormthecastle.com%2Fvideo-game-design%2Fwriting-a-video-game-script.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AVideo+game+writing\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1258\nCached time: 20180908131540\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.176 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.236 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 689/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 14603/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 810/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 3/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 5576/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase 